Hand Control Module for Smart Glasses.

Install:
python -m venv venv
# Windows:
venv\Scripts\activate
pip install -r requirements.txt

Run:
python main.py

If camera doesn't open try changing VideoCapture index (0 -> 1) or backend:
cap = cv2.VideoCapture(0, cv2.CAP_MSMF)  # alternative on Windows
On Raspberry Pi use cv2.CAP_V4L2 and ensure camera drivers are enabled.

Tweak thresholds in HandTrackingModule.recognizeGesture for your lighting/camera.




